# 3. How AI Helped Me

AI helped me in several areas during development:

## 1. Feature Planning

AI helped transform a high-level idea into a concrete React component.

Instead of only thinking:

> "I need an incident details page"

AI helped break it into:

* Modal structure
* Tabs
* Timeline component
* Evidence component
* MITRE mapping component
* User actions

This made the feature easier to implement.

---

## 2. React Development Assistance

AI helped generate and organize React components.

Examples:

* Creating modal components
* Designing component structure
* Managing UI states
* Connecting buttons and interactions
* Improving user experience

This reduced the amount of time needed to build the feature from scratch.

---

## 3. UI/UX Improvements

AI helped improve the investigation workflow by suggesting a professional security operations interface.

The final design included:

* Clear incident summaries
* Severity indicators
* Investigation tabs
* Evidence organization
* Security-focused information hierarchy

This made the application feel closer to a real Security Operations Center (SOC) dashboard.

